channel.title: Just got moparscape client
channel.description:
It has been a while since I have played moparscape, so please don't be rude or anything.
I downloaded Moparscape again after like 5 months and I cannot join even the default server, which is your own. I click start server first but it just says error connecting to server. It says Server Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?
Do I need something?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 01, 2008, 03:31:03 pm[/size][hr]Nevermind, restarted client and works fine now.
